    Scope and Contents
The subject file consists of speeches by Presidents Alex Lacy and Durwood Long, documents for the Advocacy Campaign in support of an income tax increase to aid higher education, Community College Transfer Guides, Governor's Working Groups on Accountability for Higher Education, SSU organizational charts, and SSU President Duties and Responsibilities Manual.  
  
